# Data Dictionary

## 1. User

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| name               | String           | 255              | User's full name                            |                                     | No       |              |
| email              | String           | 255              | User's email address                        | UNIQUE                              | No       |              |
| phone              | String           | 20               | User's phone number                         |                                     | Yes      |              |
| password           | String           | 255              | Hashed password                             |                                     | No       |              |
| role               | String           | 20               | User role (user, owner, delivery_boy)       | ENUM                                | No       |              |
| resetOTP           | String           | 10               | OTP for password reset                      |                                     | Yes      |              |
| resetOTPExpiry     | Date             | -                | OTP expiry time                             |                                     | Yes      |              |
| location           | GeoJSON (Point)  | [lng, lat]       | User's geolocation                          | 2dsphere index                      | Yes      | [0,0]        |
| deleted            | Boolean          | -                | Soft-delete flag                            |                                     | Yes      | false        |
| deletedAt          | Date             | -                | Deletion timestamp                          |                                     | Yes      |              |
| recoveryToken      | String           | 255              | Account recovery token                      |                                     | Yes      |              |
| recoveryRequested  | Boolean          | -                | Recovery request status                     |                                     | Yes      | false        |
| banned             | Boolean          | -                | Ban status                                  |                                     | Yes      | false        |
| bannedAt           | Date             | -                | Ban timestamp                               |                                     | Yes      |              |
| address            | String           | 255              | User's address                              |                                     | Yes      |              |
| city               | String           | 100              | City                                        |                                     | Yes      |              |
| state              | String           | 100              | State                                       |                                     | Yes      |              |
| zipCode            | String           | 20               | Zip code                                    |                                     | Yes      |              |
| lastLocationUpdate | Date             | -                | Last location update                        |                                     | Yes      |              |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 2. Owner

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| user               | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to User                           | FOREIGN KEY → User(_id)             | No       |              |
| restaurants        | [ObjectId]       | Array            | List of owned restaurants                    | FOREIGN KEY → Restaurant(_id)       | Yes      | []           |
| earnings           | Number           | Double           | Total earnings                              |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| availableBalance   | Number           | Double           | Withdrawable balance                        |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| location           | GeoJSON (Point)  | [lng, lat]       | Owner's geolocation                         | 2dsphere index                      | Yes      | [0,0]        |
| address            | String           | 255              | Owner's address                             |                                     | Yes      |              |
| lastLocationUpdate | Date             | -                | Last location update                        |                                     | Yes      |              |
| bankDetails        | Object           | -                | Bank account details                        |                                     | Yes      | See below    |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

**bankDetails**:  
- accountNumber (String, 20, default: '1234567890')  
- ifsc (String, 20, default: 'SBIN0001234')  
- beneficiaryName (String, 100, default: 'Test Owner')

---

## 3. Restaurant

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| name               | String           | 255              | Restaurant name                             |                                     | No       |              |
| description        | String           | 500              | Description                                 |                                     | Yes      |              |
| cuisine            | String           | 100              | Cuisine type                                |                                     | Yes      |              |
| address            | String           | 255              | Address                                     |                                     | No       |              |
| phone              | String           | 20               | Phone number                                |                                     | Yes      |              |
| image              | String           | 255              | Image URL                                   |                                     | No       |              |
| isOpen             | Boolean          | -                | Open status                                 |                                     | Yes      | true         |
| rating             | Number           | Double           | Average rating                              | Derived                             | Yes      | 0            |
| deliveryTime       | String           | 20               | Estimated delivery time                     |                                     | Yes      |              |
| minOrder           | Number           | Double           | Minimum order amount                        |                                     | Yes      | 10           |
| openingTime        | String           | 5 (HH:mm)        | Opening time                                |                                     | Yes      |              |
| openingPeriod      | String           | 2                | Opening period (AM/PM)                      | ENUM                                | Yes      |              |
| closingTime        | String           | 5 (HH:mm)        | Closing time                                |                                     | Yes      |              |
| closingPeriod      | String           | 2                | Closing period (AM/PM)                      | ENUM                                | Yes      |              |
| location           | GeoJSON (Point)  | [lng, lat]       | Geolocation                                 | 2dsphere index                      | Yes      | [0,0]        |
| city               | String           | 100              | City                                        |                                     | Yes      |              |
| state              | String           | 100              | State                                       |                                     | Yes      |              |
| zipCode            | String           | 20               | Zip code                                    |                                     | Yes      |              |
| owner              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Owner                          | FOREIGN KEY → Owner(_id)            | Yes      |              |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |
| deleted            | Boolean          | -                | Soft-delete flag                            |                                     | Yes      | false        |
| deletedAt          | Date             | -                | Deletion timestamp                          |                                     | Yes      |              |
| deletedBy          | String           | 100              | Deleted by (user/admin)                     |                                     | Yes      |              |

---

## 4. MenuItem

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| name               | String           | 255              | Item name                                   |                                     | No       |              |
| description        | String           | 500              | Item description                            |                                     | Yes      |              |
| price              | Number           | Double           | Item price                                  |                                     | No       |              |
| image              | String           | 255              | Image URL                                   |                                     | No       |              |
| category           | String           | 100              | Category                                    |                                     | Yes      |              |
| restaurant         | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Restaurant                     | FOREIGN KEY → Restaurant(_id)       | No       |              |
| isVeg              | Boolean          | -                | Vegetarian flag                             |                                     | Yes      | true         |
| isAvailable        | Boolean          | -                | Availability flag                           |                                     | Yes      | true         |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 5. Order

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| user               | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to User                           | FOREIGN KEY → User(_id)             | No       |              |
| restaurant         | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Restaurant                     | FOREIGN KEY → Restaurant(_id)       | No       |              |
| items              | Array            | -                | Ordered items (menuItem, name, qty, price)  | FOREIGN KEY → MenuItem(_id)         | No       |              |
| deliveryAddress    | String           | 255              | Delivery address                            |                                     | No       |              |
| totalAmount        | Number           | Double           | Total order amount                          |                                     | No       |              |
| ownerEarning       | Number           | Double           | Owner's earning from order                  |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| subtotal           | Number           | Double           | Subtotal before discount                    |                                     | Yes      |              |
| discountAmount     | Number           | Double           | Discount applied                            |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| promoCode          | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to PromoCode                      | FOREIGN KEY → PromoCode(_id)        | Yes      |              |
| specialInstructions| String           | 500              | Special instructions                        |                                     | Yes      |              |
| paymentMethod      | String           | 20               | Payment method                              | ENUM                                | Yes      | 'cod'        |
| paymentStatus      | String           | 20               | Payment status                              | ENUM                                | Yes      | 'unpaid'     |
| razorpayOrderId    | String           | 50               | Razorpay order ID                           |                                     | Yes      |              |
| razorpayPaymentId  | String           | 50               | Razorpay payment ID                         |                                     | Yes      |              |
| razorpaySignature  | String           | 100              | Razorpay signature                          |                                     | Yes      |              |
| status             | String           | 20               | Order status                                | ENUM                                | Yes      | 'placed'     |
| deliveryStatus     | String           | 20               | Delivery status                             | ENUM                                | Yes      | 'assigned'   |
| deliveryBoy        | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to DeliveryBoy                    | FOREIGN KEY → DeliveryBoy(_id)      | Yes      |              |
| acceptedAt         | Date             | -                | Order accepted timestamp                    |                                     | Yes      |              |
| deliveryOTP        | String           | 10               | Delivery OTP                                |                                     | Yes      |              |
| deliveryOTPExpiry  | Date             | -                | OTP expiry                                  |                                     | Yes      |              |
| deliveryOTPAttempts| Number           | Int              | OTP attempts                                |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| isOTPVerified      | Boolean          | -                | OTP verified flag                           |                                     | Yes      | false        |
| deliveredAt        | Date             | -                | Delivery timestamp                          |                                     | Yes      |              |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 6. DeliveryBoy

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| user               | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to User                           | FOREIGN KEY → User(_id)             | No       |              |
| phone              | String           | 20               | Phone number                                |                                     | Yes      |              |
| vehicleType        | String           | 20               | Vehicle type                                | ENUM                                | No       |              |
| licenseNumber      | String           | 50               | License number                              |                                     | No       |              |
| isAvailable        | Boolean          | -                | Availability flag                           |                                     | Yes      | true         |
| location           | GeoJSON (Point)  | [lng, lat]       | Geolocation                                 | 2dsphere index                      | Yes      | [0,0]        |
| address            | String           | 255              | Address                                     |                                     | Yes      |              |
| lastLocationUpdate | Date             | -                | Last location update                        |                                     | Yes      |              |
| currentOrders      | [ObjectId]       | Array            | Current orders                              | FOREIGN KEY → Order(_id)            | Yes      | []           |
| earnings           | Number           | Double           | Total earnings                              |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| availableBalance   | Number           | Double           | Withdrawable balance                        |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| earningsBreakdown  | Object           | -                | Earnings breakdown (today, week, etc.)       |                                     | Yes      | See below    |
| deliveryHistory    | Array            | -                | Delivery history                            | Embedded subdocs                    | Yes      | []           |
| totalDeliveries    | Number           | Int              | Total deliveries                            |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| rating             | Number           | Double           | Average rating                              | Derived                             | Yes      | 0            |
| totalRatings       | Number           | Int              | Total ratings                               |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| reviews            | [ObjectId]       | Array            | Reviews received                            | FOREIGN KEY → Review(_id)           | Yes      | []           |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

**earningsBreakdown**:  
- today, todayOrders, thisWeek, weeklyOrders, thisMonth, monthlyOrders, pending (Number, default: 0)  
- lastResetDate (String, default: today)

---

## 7. Review

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| user               | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to User                           | FOREIGN KEY → User(_id)             | No       |              |
| restaurant         | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Restaurant                     | FOREIGN KEY → Restaurant(_id)       | No       |              |
| order              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Order                          | FOREIGN KEY → Order(_id)            | Yes      |              |
| rating             | Number           | Int (1-5)        | Restaurant rating                           | CHECK (1-5)                         | No       |              |
| comment            | String           | 500              | Review comment                              |                                     | Yes      |              |
| deliveryBoy        | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to DeliveryBoy                    | FOREIGN KEY → DeliveryBoy(_id)      | Yes      |              |
| deliveryRating     | Number           | Int (1-5)        | Delivery rating                             | CHECK (1-5)                         | Yes      |              |
| deliveryComment    | String           | 500              | Delivery review comment                     |                                     | Yes      |              |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 8. PromoCode

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| code               | String           | 20               | Promo code                                  | UNIQUE, UPPERCASE                   | No       |              |
| restaurant         | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Restaurant                     | FOREIGN KEY → Restaurant(_id)       | No       |              |
| owner              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Owner                          | FOREIGN KEY → Owner(_id)            | No       |              |
| discountPercentage | Number           | Int (0-100)      | Discount percentage                         | CHECK (0-100)                       | Yes      | 10           |
| description        | String           | 255              | Description                                 |                                     | Yes      |              |
| isActive           | Boolean          | -                | Active status                               |                                     | Yes      | true         |
| usageLimit         | Number           | Int              | Usage limit                                 |                                     | Yes      | null         |
| usageCount         | Number           | Int              | Usage count                                 |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| minOrderAmount     | Number           | Double           | Minimum order amount                        |                                     | Yes      | 0            |
| expiryDate         | Date             | -                | Expiry date                                 |                                     | Yes      | null         |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 9. Payout

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| owner              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Owner                          | FOREIGN KEY → Owner(_id)            | No       |              |
| amount             | Number           | Double           | Payout amount                               |                                     | No       |              |
| status             | String           | 20               | Payout status                               | ENUM                                | Yes      | 'pending'    |
| razorpayPayoutId   | String           | 50               | Razorpay payout ID                          |                                     | Yes      |              |
| method             | String           | 20               | Payout method                               |                                     | Yes      | 'bank_transfer'|
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 10. Transaction

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| owner              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Owner                          | FOREIGN KEY → Owner(_id)            | Yes      |              |
| deliveryBoy        | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to DeliveryBoy                    | FOREIGN KEY → DeliveryBoy(_id)      | Yes      |              |
| amount             | Number           | Double           | Transaction amount                          |                                     | No       |              |
| type               | String           | 20               | Transaction type                            | ENUM                                | No       |              |
| status             | String           | 20               | Transaction status                          | ENUM                                | Yes      | 'success'    |
| referenceId        | String           | 50               | Reference ID (order/payment/payout)         |                                     | Yes      |              |
| description        | String           | 255              | Description                                 |                                     | Yes      |              |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---

## 11. Suggestion

| Column Name        | Data Type         | Size/Format      | Description                                 | Constraints                        | Nullable | Default Value |
|--------------------|------------------|------------------|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------|----------|--------------|
| _id                | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Unique identifier (Primary Key)             | PRIMARY KEY                         | No       | Auto-gen     |
| order              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Order                          | FOREIGN KEY → Order(_id)            | No       |              |
| restaurant         | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Restaurant                     | FOREIGN KEY → Restaurant(_id)       | No       |              |
| owner              | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to Owner                          | FOREIGN KEY → Owner(_id)            | No       |              |
| user               | ObjectId         | 12 bytes         | Reference to User                           | FOREIGN KEY → User(_id)             | No       |              |
| text               | String           | 500              | Suggestion text                             |                                     | Yes      | ''           |
| createdAt          | Date             | -                | Creation timestamp                          | AUDIT FIELD                         | No       | Date.now     |

---
